name: Jupiter_(cat)
text:
Jupiter (cat)
Jupiter was a cat that belonged to Laura Palmer.
During a dream Laura had on the night of July 23, 1983, she encountered a man "with long hair and very large, callused hands" who told her that he had Jupiter.
Laura stopped writing in her diary between September 15, 1983 and October 3 of the next year. In the interim, Jupiter was hit by a car after chasing a mouse into the road in front of the Palmer house.
